ANC treasurer-general Paul Mashatile has added a hand to several hands that are pushing the drowning EFF leader Julius Malema and his red brigade deeper into the red sea of legal woes. This after Mashatile filed R2m in lawsuits against Malema, the EFF and EFF Gauteng leader Mandisa Mashego for defamation of character after calling him a thief, among other names. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD